data.form:
<script>
    window.App.IndexController.reopen({
        isSubmitting: false,
        jokeRecipient: "",
        jokesChecked:[],
        
        jokes: Ember.computed('jsonTask', function() {
           var model = jsonTask.FACTS.apidata_data.result;
           var responses = [];
           var headers = {};
           model.questions.forEach (function(question, index){
               headers[question.id] = question.question;
           })

           model.responses.forEach(function(response, index){
               if (response.completed=="1"){
                   var answer = response.answers;
                   var response = {};
                   for (var key in headers) {
                       response[headers[key]] = answer[key];
                   }
                   responses.push(response);
               }
           })
           
           var result = [];
           
           responses.forEach(function(response, index){
               result.push(response["Tell a joke"]);
           })
           
           return result;
           
        }),
        
        actions: {
            submitAction: function(){
                this.set("isSubmitting", true );
                $("#emberForm").submit();
                return true;
            }
        }
    });
</script>
<script type="text/x-handlebars" data-template-name="index">
    {{#sc-container}}
    
        {{sc-dropdown label="Which one?" content=jokes name="joke"}}
            
        {{sc-input label="Friend email" name="jokeRecipient" value=jokeRecipient}}
        
        {{#sc-buttons}}
            {{#sc-button action="submitAction"}}Send{{/sc-button}}
        {{/sc-buttons}} 
        
        {{#sc-overlay active=isSubmitting}}
          {{sc-loading center=true}}
        {{/sc-overlay}}
            
    {{/sc-container}}
</script>
